Title: SQS Queue Backlog / Message Aging – Runbook

Symptoms:
- CloudWatch alert: Queue depth high
- CloudWatch alert: Oldest message age high

Triage:
- Check CloudWatch metrics for backlog and age
- Check consumer service health (pods / ECS tasks / StreamSets jobs)
- Review recent deployments

Mitigation:
- Scale consumers (HPA / ECS scaling)
- Restart stuck workers
- Validate downstream dependencies
- Purge queue ONLY with approval

Escalation:
- Platform On-call
- Data Cloud team

Links:
- CloudWatch Dashboard: <link>
- Logs: <link>
- Queue(s): <names>




for i in {1..25}; do
  aws sqs send-message \
    --queue-url https://sqs.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/ACCOUNT_ID/YOUR_QUEUE_NAME \
    --message-body "test-message-$i"
done



